Julián Mateos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juli%C3%A1n_Mateos 0 Julián Mateos (15 January 1938 – 27 December 1996) was a Spanish actor and film producer. He appeared in 48 films and television shows between 1960 and 1980. He starred in the film The Robbers, which was entered into the 12th Berlin International Film Festival.
